,{"word":"tale","count":1},{"word":"mind","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"prank","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"tacet","count":1},{"word":"discord","count":1},{"word":"variant","count":1},{"word":"rumors","count":1},{"word":"swirling","count":1},{"word":"folks","count":1},{"word":"jittery","count":1},{"word":"escalate","count":1},{"word":"reached","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"counting","count":1},{"word":"crack","count":1},{"word":"case","count":1},{"word":"wide","count":1},{"word":"open","count":1},{"word":"deal","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"pay","count":1},{"word":"takes","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"goosebumps","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"uncover","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"chat","count":1},{"word":"names","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hey, Rover! Took you long enough to get here!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Things are getting awfully strange around the mine lately. Figured you're just the one to untangle this mess.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"With your knack for solving mysteries, you'll figure this out in no time!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"I don't know if you've ever heard of it, but there's a special folktale in Jinzhou...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Word has it, there's this mysterious Arcane Artist whose paintings come to life as they paint, as if each brushstroke has a life of its own.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Once their canvas dries, whatever they've painted leaps right off the page. Mythical creatures, the whole shebang—all real as day!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"The thing is, anyone who might've seen these paintings? Well, they vanish into thin air...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"I've never heard of such unique Forte.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Lately, I've been receiving reports about eerie monsters wandering the mine at midnight. Some witnesses even ran into them more than once!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"These monsters, they look like paintings from a distance. But approach them and they're as docile as can be.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Reading these reports, I couldn't shake the tale of the Arcane Artist from my mind.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Sure, some say it's just a prank or some new Tacet Discord variant...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"But with rumors swirling, folks are getting jittery. Can't let things escalate. That's why I reached out to you.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Great! Counting on you to crack this case wide open.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Deal! I'll pay whatever it takes to keep the goosebumps coming. I can't wait for you to uncover the truth!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Oh, and you might want to chat up the witnesses. Got their names right here for you.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000}]}